export const homeObjOne = {
    id: 'about',
    lightBg: false,
    lightText: true,
    lightTextDesc: true,
    topLine: 'Grain Units Calculator',
    headLine: 'Why is this our choice?',
    description: 'In 2012, 1.5 million people died from diabetes worldwide. Most of the people who died from diabetes died prematurely from complications of diabetes mellitus, that is, not reaching the age of 70. Such complications appear when a person does not devote enough time and attention to their nutrition, does not adjust the correct doses of insulin, thereby not monitoring blood sugar levels. As we can see, the consequences can be fatal.',
    buttonLabel: 'Learn More',
    imgStart: false,
    img: require('../../images/svg-2.svg').default,
    alt: 'img',
    dark: true,
    primary: true,
    darkText: false
};

export const homeObjTwo = {
    id: 'discover',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Grain Units Calculator',
    headLine: 'Motivation to help in such an important point.',
    description: 'According to the national register of the Republic of Kazakhstan, the incidence of diabetes mellitus in the Republic is high; in terms of medical and social indicators, it takes 3rd place after cardiovascular and oncological diseases. The steady increase in patients with diabetes in Kazakhstan over the past decades, as shown in Diagram 1, indicates the need to develop a program for the control and prevention of diabetes, as well as regular promotion of a healthy lifestyle, proper nutrition, etc.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get into',
    imgStart: true,
    img: require('../../images/svg-1.svg').default,
    alt: 'img',
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: true
};

export const homeObjThree = {
    id: 'signup',
    lightBg: true,
    lightText: false,
    lightTextDesc: false,
    topLine: 'Grain Units Calculator',
    headLine: 'How can we affect people life?',
    description: 'We want not only to help people with diabetes to control sugar, but also to make sure that people do not adjust their diet to insulin, reducing the variety of their food, but the amount of insulin adjusted to the persons diet.',
    buttonLabel: 'Get Started',
    imgStart: false,
    img: require('../../images/svg-3.svg').default,
    alt: 'img',
    dark: false,
    primary: false,
    darkText: true
}
